{"tid":1670654,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone SE2 明年初投產   郭明錤：將採用 LCP 天線，改善網絡連線能力","createTime":"2019-10-23T05:18:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T14:21:59.000Z","uid":109923,"like":5,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"494f48aac45867fd5f9104eadb84c8c756f9251d","tid":1670654,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:18:33.000Z","msg":"有傳聞指 Apple 將會在 2020 年首季，推出 iPhone SE 的後繼型號，新機將會採用類似 iPhone 8 的機身，搭配 A13 Bionic 處理器和 3GB RAM。著名分析師郭明錤日前撰文，估計 Appe 將會在 iPhone SE2 採用名為 LCP（Liquid Crystal Polymer）的天線以改善網絡連線能力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bH6iCnj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbH6iCnj.jpg&h=af09dc25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLCP 是一種柔性有機物料，擁有熱膨脹度低和極小頻率損耗的特性，令這種物料非常適合應用於無線天線，此外，它的構造相當緊密，而且高度耐火。LCP 以往多數用於汽車感應器、揚聲器驅動器和光纖產品，郭明錤表示 Apple 的供應商 Murata 將會負責供應 iPhone SE2 的 LCP 天線。<br />\n<br />\n郭明錤提到 LCP 天線會在明年出貨予 Apple，以配合 iPhone SE2 明年年初投產。早前有傳聞指 iPhone SE2 將會有太空灰、銀色和紅色機身選擇，基本 64GB 儲存型號的定價為 399 美元（約 3,129 港元）。<br />\n<br />\n來源：gsmarena"},{"pid":"f07ef838ac53d7ed27210e0d9ab4939ae6bbc2a8","tid":1670654,"uid":17794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:26:26.000Z","msg":"哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽住先"},{"pid":"d77005061ac9b460d16c4455345e95a5b4ef5680","tid":1670654,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T05:26:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c710755088cd9f9fe0db14c67d7014f55c5d839f","tid":1670654,"uid":159448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T06:50:12.000Z","msg":"同我推返上一次啲se2 post出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a30544d9218d60cf91abb4452f9bb62fcfb048b","tid":1670654,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T07:39:22.000Z","msg":"有傳聞🖕🏼"},{"pid":"e6fe6d1a88b4eeb073e2d9ffdfc0221c9e